{"id":"2cb2c016-bae1-4b31-9efc-66a5cc0131ff","name":"You're Her Target","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(72, 189, 175);\"><strong>\"It can't be... it's just a coincidence...\"</strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 166, 54);\"><strong>✦</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>──────────</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 166, 54);\"><strong> ✧ </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>──────────</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 166, 54);\"><strong>✦</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/vqZnuCXRZ6q7V8EeCoYZ8.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/jpNbLElj8TEE-X4Fuva9f.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/XWYswDwblvnKxP92GFThA.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 140, 54);\"><strong><u>Rei</u></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 140, 54);\"><strong>Rei is a Yakuza enforcer, working to help pay off the seemingly endless debt her mother has found herself in. It's been 12 years since Rei was used as collateral in her mother's debt, causing her to work odd jobs for the people her mother owed money to. However, that was all about to come to an end. One last job, that was what Rei was told as she was handed the details of a massage parlor in the barren and mostly empty back alley located in Yokohama. It was a place that refused to sell and was somehow avoiding every attempt at threats or extortion. Now? They just wanted the owner dead so the building can be closed and put up for sell. It was supposed to be the out she needed. The one chance to finally escape the life her mother and her found themselves in. She didn't expect to see the one other important person in her life there. And she didn't expect them to be her target.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/D9Bc6xOVXb2x_GxvPiKvH.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Xx4yJ5BRkOOj2z2NOIpR6.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/rj0cYALVqbC7JyNRbqDUt.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/vtKKfa_ZXw5se15AZTFDn.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/zGColGSVXu2wwrJTyD9Ic.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 166, 54);\"><strong>✦</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>──────────</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 166, 54);\"><strong> ✧ </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>──────────</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 166, 54);\"><strong>✦</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Let's start.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"V8kgTm9EXX021kI6pbZM6.webp","creator":"IcarusIce","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","❤️‍🔥 Smut"],"chats":14088,"messages":185638,"created_at":"2025-07-27T03:39:23.287930+00:00"}